lead_paragraph: A $150 million high-tech retractable roof for the Arthur Ashe Stadium court looked like money well spent as play went ahead as scheduled on Thursday, despite steady rain at the U.S. Open.

headline.print_headline: Players Stay Dry but Noise Rains Down at U.S. Open
